## 🔹 Array Instructions (0x40-0x43)

### 1️⃣ ARRALLOC (0x40) - 배열 할당

```rust
fn exec_arralloc(&mut self) -> Result<(), String> {
    // Pop array size
    let size = self.pop()?;

    // Get current heap pointer
    let array_addr = self.heap_ptr;

    // Check heap bounds (heap: 0x5000 - 0xFFFD, ~20K words)
    if array_addr + size + 1 >= 0xFFFE {
        return Err("ARRALLOC: Heap overflow".to_string());
    }

    // Write metadata (length)
    self.memory.write(array_addr, size)?;

    // Initialize array elements to 0
    for i in 0..size {
        self.memory.write(array_addr + 1 + i as usize, 0)?;
    }

    // Update heap pointer
    self.heap_ptr += (size + 1) as usize;

    // Push array address
    self.push(array_addr as u64)?;

    Ok(())
}
```

**스택 동작**:
```
Before: [size, ...]
After:  [array_address, ...]
```

**바이트코드 형식**:
```
[0x40]
```

---

### 2️⃣ ARRGET (0x41) - 배열 요소 읽기

```rust
fn exec_arrget(&mut self) -> Result<(), String> {
    // Pop index
    let index = self.pop()?;

    // Pop array address
    let array_addr = self.pop()? as usize;

    // Read array length
    let length = self.memory.read(array_addr)?;

    // Check bounds
    if index >= length {
        return Err(format!("ARRGET: Index out of bounds: {} >= {}", index, length));
    }

    // Read element
    let element = self.memory.read(array_addr + 1 + index as usize)?;

    // Push element
    self.push(element)?;

    Ok(())
}
```

**스택 동작**:
```
Before: [array_address, index, ...]
After:  [element, ...]
```

**바이트코드 형식**:
```
[0x41]
```

