### 4️⃣ ARRLEN (0x43) - 배열 길이

```rust
fn exec_arrlen(&mut self) -> Result<(), String> {
    // Pop array address
    let array_addr = self.pop()? as usize;

    // Read and validate address
    if array_addr >= 0x5000 {
        return Err("ARRLEN: Invalid array address".to_string());
    }

    // Read array length
    let length = self.memory.read(array_addr)?;

    // Push length
    self.push(length)?;

    Ok(())
}
```

**스택 동작**:
```
Before: [array_address, ...]
After:  [length, ...]
```

**바이트코드 형식**:
```
[0x43]
```

