## 🔶 String Instructions (0x50-0x53)

### 5️⃣ STRALLOC (0x50) - 문자열 할당

```rust
fn exec_stralloc(&mut self) -> Result<(), String> {
    // Pop string length
    let length = self.pop()?;

    // Get current heap pointer
    let string_addr = self.heap_ptr;

    // Check heap bounds
    if string_addr + length + 1 >= 0xFFFE {
        return Err("STRALLOC: Heap overflow".to_string());
    }

    // Write metadata (length)
    self.memory.write(string_addr, length)?;

    // Initialize string to 0 (null bytes)
    for i in 0..length {
        self.memory.write(string_addr + 1 + i as usize, 0)?;
    }

    // Update heap pointer
    self.heap_ptr += (length + 1) as usize;

    // Push string address
    self.push(string_addr as u64)?;

    Ok(())
}
```

**스택 동작**:
```
Before: [length, ...]
After:  [string_address, ...]
```

**바이트코드 형식**:
```
[0x50]
```

---

### 6️⃣ STRGET (0x51) - 문자 읽기

```rust
fn exec_strget(&mut self) -> Result<(), String> {
    // Pop index
    let index = self.pop()?;

    // Pop string address
    let string_addr = self.pop()? as usize;

    // Read string length
    let length = self.memory.read(string_addr)?;

    // Check bounds
    if index >= length {
        return Err(format!("STRGET: Index out of bounds: {} >= {}", index, length));
    }

    // Read character
    let char_val = self.memory.read(string_addr + 1 + index as usize)?;

    // Push character
    self.push(char_val)?;

    Ok(())
}
```

**스택 동작**:
```
Before: [string_address, index, ...]
After:  [char_value, ...]
```

**바이트코드 형식**:
```
[0x51]
```

